            <h3 style="margin-left: 8px;">Crispy Fish Sauce Chicken Noodles:</h3>
            <p>
              Description: Cook rice noodles according to package instructions. Set aside.
              Mix fish sauce, soy sauce, oyster sauce, and sugar in a bowl. Set aside.
              Stir-fry chicken in 1 tablespoon of oil until crispy. Remove and set aside.
              Sauté garlic, onion, and bell pepper in the same skillet.
              Add cooked noodles and sauce to the skillet. Cook for 2-3 minutes.
              Return chicken to the skillet and cook for another 2-3 minutes.
            </p>
