            <h3 style="margin-left: 8px;"> Berry Yogurt Parfait:</h3>
            <p>
              In a glass or a mason jar, layer the Greek yogurt, mixed berries, and granola.
              Repeat the layers until all the ingredients are used, finishing with a layer of granola on top.
              Serve the berry yogurt parfait immediately, or refrigerate for a couple of hours to allow the flavors to meld.
              Enjoy this refreshing and nutritious treat!
            </p>
