          <div class="recipe-content">
            <h3 style="margin-left: 8px;"> Grilled Cheese Sandwich:</h3>
            <p>
              Description: A classic comfort food that is crispy on the outside and gooey on the inside.
              Ingredients:2 slices of bread, Butter(softend),2 slices of your favorite cheese (e.g., cheddar, Swiss, American)
              Instructions:
              Heat a skillet or griddle over medium heat.
              Spread butter on one side of each bread slice.
              Place one slice of bread, butter-side down, on the heated surface.
              Add the cheese slices on top of the bread.
              Cover with the second slice of bread, butter-side up.
              Cook until the bottom slice of bread is golden brown and the cheese starts to melt.
              Flip the sandwich and cook until the other side is golden brown and the cheese is completely melted.
              Remove from heat, slice diagonally if desired, and serve hot.
            </p>
          </div>
